Crypto%20Strategic%20Reserve%26quot%3B%20that%20would%20include%20the%20cryptocurrencies%20Ripple%2C%20Solana%2C%20and%20Cardano.%20In%20a%20follow-up%20post%2C%20Trump%20said%20that%20Bitcoin%20and%20Ethereum%20would%20also%20%26quot%3Bbe%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20reserve.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20strategic%20reserve%20is%20a%20pool%20of%20resources%20that%20a%20government%20withholds%20from%20normal%20use%20to%20be%20used%20in%20times%20of%20crisis%20or%20supply%20chain%20disruptions.%20The%20United%20States%20has%20other%20strategic%20reserves%2C%20like%20the%20Strategic%20Petroleum%20Reserve%2C%20which%20holds%20oil%20in%2028%20refineries%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ealong%20the%20Gulf%20Coast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMy%20Executive%20Order%20on%20Digital%20Assets%20directed%20the%20Presidential%20Working%20Group%20to%20move%20forward%20on%20a%20Crypto%20Strategic%20Reserve%20that%20includes%20XRP%2C%20SOL%2C%20and%20ADA%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20in%20the%20post.%20%26quot%3BI%20will%20make%20sure%20the%20U.S.%20is%20the%20Crypto%20Capital%20of%20the%20World.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20crypto-tracking%20site%20CoinGecko%2C%20Ripple%20jumped%20over%2030%25%2C%20while%20Solana%20and%20Cardano%20rose%20by%2021%25%20and%2061%25%20after%20Trump's%20announcement.%20Bitcoin%20also%20rose%20by%209%25%2C%20and%20Ethereum%20jumped%2012%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20of%20Sunday%20afternoon%2C%20Ethereum%20was%20trading%20at%20%242%2C500%20and%20Bitcoin%20was%20trading%20at%20%2494%2C069%2C%20according%20to%20CoinGecko.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20announcement%20followed%20a%20pledge%20he%20made%20in%20July%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-bitcoin-stance-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBitcoin%202024%20conference%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20where%20he%20vowed%20to%20keep%20all%20the%20cryptocurrency%20owned%20by%20the%20federal%20government%20%E2%80%94%20most%20of%20which%20was%20seized%20by%20law%20enforcement%20%E2%80%94%20in%20a%20%26quot%3Bnational%20Bitcoin%20stockpile.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20post%20on%20Sunday%20was%20his%20first%20mention%20of%20a%20crypto%20reserve%20rather%20than%20a%20crypto%20stockpile.%20A%20crypto%20reserve%20involves%20actively%20buying%20cryptocurrency%2C%20while%20a%20stockpile%20would%20hold%20cryptocurrency%20the%20government%20already%20owns.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22afac45a6-3aef-4e3c-8abe-77db23652448%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EFrom%20'scam'%20to%20fan%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ETrump's%20effort%20to%20create%20the%20first%20US%20crypto%20strategic%20reserve%20marks%20the%20apex%20of%20his%20180-degree%20turn%20on%20cryptocurrency.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20his%20first%20term%20in%20office%2C%20Trump%20called%20crypto%20a%20%26quot%3Bscam.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20Bitcoin%20and%20other%20Cryptocurrencies%2C%20which%20are%20not%20money%2C%20and%20whose%20value%20is%20highly%20volatile%20and%20based%20on%20thin%20air%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20Twitter%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrump%20appeared%20to%20have%20a%20change%20of%20heart%20during%20the%202024%20presidential%20election%2C%20even%20launching%20his%20own%20crypto-banking%20venture%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdonald-trump-going-for-crypto-bro-vote-world-liberty-financial-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EWorld%20Liberty%20Financial%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20in%20October.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we%20don't%20do%20it%2C%20China%20will%20do%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Trump%20said%20at%20the%20time%2C%20referring%20to%20embracing%20crypto%20as%20a%20mainstream%20currency.%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20be%20the%20biggest%20and%20the%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20his%20election%2C%20Trump%20and%20first%20lady%20Melania%20Trump%20even%20released%20their%20own%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-launches-cryptocurrency-days-b