B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BArtistes%20Are%20Not%20Slaves%20Of%20Congress%26quot%3B%3A%20BJP%20Rips%20Into%20DK%20Shivakumar%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EKarnataka%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20DK%20Shivakumar's%20%26quot%3Bnuts%20and%20bolts%26quot%3B%20comment%20about%20cine%20artistes%20has%20drawn%20indignant%20protests%20from%20the%20state's%20Opposition%20BJP.%20The%20state's%20Leader%20of%20the%20Opposition%20R%20Ashoka%20said%20it%20was%20up%20to%20the%20artistes%20whether%20they%20join%20a%20political%20protest%20or%20not%20and%20it%20showed%20a%20%26quot%3Bbad%20mindset%26quot%3B%20on%20his%20part.%20%26quot%3BArtists%20are%20not%20slaves%20of%20the%20Congress%20party%2C%20and%20despite%20their%20support%2C%20movies%20are%20not%20succeeding%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BArtistes%20are%20not%20your%20party%20workers.%20Don't%20treat%20artists%20the%20way%20you%20treat%20your%20party%20workers.%20Learn%20to%20respect%20artists%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20rough%20translation%20of%20his%20vernacular%20post%20on%20social%20media%20platform%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDear%20DCM%20DK%20Shivakumar%2C%20it%20is%20not%20upto%20the%20Congress%20party's%20discretion%20whether%20or%20not%20film%20artists%20will%20come%20to%20the%20political%20march.%20Your%20statement%20that%20artists%20who%20march%20for%20the%20Congress%20party%20will%20get%20recognition%2C%20otherwise%20they%20will%20not%2C%20does%20not%20bring%20glory%20to%20your%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThreats%20and%20hooliganism%20have%20no%20place%20in%20democracy.%20The%20BJP%20government%20had%20provided%20significant%20support%20to%20the%20film%20industry.%20If%20actor%20Ambareesh%20were%20alive%20today%2C%20he%20would%20have%20given%20a%20fitting%20response.%20The%20film%20industry%20must%20condemn%20these%20statements%2C%20as%20they%20are%20an%20insult%20to%20artists.%20D.K.%20Shivakumar%20should%20apologize%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENikhil%20Kumaraswamy%20of%20Janata%20Dal%20Secular%20said%20it%20was%20the%20prerogative%20of%20actors%20to%20support%20any%20movement%20launched%20in%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BSome%20might%20have%20decided%20against%20participating%20to%20stop%20identifying%20themselves%20with%20any%20party%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Saturday%2C%20Mr%20Shivakumar%2C%20in%20an%20outburst%20at%20the%20inauguration%20of%20Bengaluru%20International%20Film%20Festival%2C%20slammed%20the%20film%20fraternity%20for%20its%20thin%20turnout%20at%20the%20event%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Congress's%20Mekedatu%20padayatra.%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20government%20does%20not%20grant%20permission%20for%20shooting%2C%20they%20cannot%20make%20a%20film.%20They%20cannot%20proceed%20with%20shooting.%20I%20also%20know%20exactly%20where%20to%20tighten%20the%20nuts%20and%20bolts%2C%20please%20understand%20that%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20had%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThen%20he%20had%20doubled%20down%20on%20the%20comment%20in%20face%20of%20criticism.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20film%20festival%20is%20not%20a%20private%20event%20of%20some%20politicians%20and%20some%20actors.%20It%20is%20a%20programme%20for%20the%20entire%20industry%2C%20yet%20only%20a%20few%20actors%20have%20participated.%20Why%20should%20the%20government%20conduct%20the%20film%20festival%20if%20the%20actors%2C%20directors%2C%20producers%20and%20exhibitors%20are%20not%20interested%3F%20Treat%20it%20as%20an%20appeal%20or%20as%20a%20caution%2C%20but%20the%20film%20fraternity%20must%20attend%20such%20events%20in%20the%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20read%20a%20statement%20from%20his%20office.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20also%20clarified%20his%20stand%20about%20the%20foot%20march%2C%20underscoring%20it%20was%20about%20ensuring%20drinking%20water%20for%20Bengaluru.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMekedatu%20padayatra%20was%20to%20get%20drinking%20water%20for%20Bengaluru.%20It%20was