%20money%20than%20we%20had%20anticipated%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frv-camper-hidden-costs-2020-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ecosts%20of%20traveling%20around%20in%20an%20RV%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20are%20mainly%20related%20to%20gas%20and%20campsites.%20We%20soon%20realized%20that%20the%20speed%20at%20which%20we%20were%20traveling%20resulted%20in%20us%20burning%20money%20at%20a%20rate%20greater%20than%20we%20had%20anticipated%20in%20our%20gas-guzzling%20Toyota%20Tundra%20towing%20our%2022-foot%20travel%20trailer.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20we%20could%20save%20on%20campsite%20costs%20with%20our%20memberships%20and%20boondocking%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20gas%20resulted%20in%20us%20dipping%20into%20our%20savings%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20lifestyle.%20Additionally%2C%20while%20at%20home%2C%20we%20shopped%20at%20Costco%20and%20cooked%20in%20bulk%20to%20meal%20prep%20and%20freeze%20food%2C%20but%20on%20the%20road%2C%20we%20bought%20smaller%20quantities%20of%20groceries%2C%20which%20were%20more%20expensive.%20There%20was%20also%20the%20novelty%20of%20buying%20fresh%20local%20produce%2C%20even%20when%20it%20was%20three%20times%20more%20expensive%20%E2%80%94%20after%20all%20who%20could%20pass%20up%20the%20allure%20of%20buying%20fresh%20eggs%20and%20bread%20from%20the%20farm%20you're%20spending%20the%20night%20at%3F%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22605bca33-1748-4e9c-9dbd-6180138029ce%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3EWe%20met%20so%20many%20people%20who%20cared%20for%20our%20baby%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3ELooking%20back%20at%20our%20big%20RV%20trip%2C%20I%20think%20fondly%20not%20just%20of%20the%20sights%20we%20saw%2C%20like%20the%20painted%20desert%20in%20Arizona%20and%20the%20Catskills%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20the%20people%20we%20met%20along%20the%20way.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Mom%20holding%20baby%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1e3d569253ccddf97e911%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222160%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20packed%20months'%20worth%20of%20clothes%20for%20her%20son%20since%20he%20grew%20so%20much%20during%20the%20trip.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhen%20we%20stopped%20for%20a%20night%20at%20a%20Vino%20Veritas%20in%20Cleveland%2C%20we%20discovered%20it%20had%20once%20been%20a%20school%2C%20and%20the%20property%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20winery%20and%20hobby%20farm.%20and%20also%20allowed%20a%20couple%20of%20RVs%20to%20park%20on-site%20in%20exchange%20for%20purchasing%20something%20from%20the%20winery.%20The%20owner%20took%20my%20son%20around%20to%20see%20his%20pigs%2C%20goats%2C%20geese%2C%20and%20ducks.%20In%20the%20mornings%2C%20his%20dogs%20would%20join%20us%20outside%20for%20breakfast%20at%20the%20picnic%20tables%2C%20and%20at%20night%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20dodged%20a%20family%20of%20skunks%20on%20the%20way%20to%20the%20restroom.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Idaho%20we%20stopped%20at%20a%20local%20library%2C%20one%20of%20many%20we%20stopped%20at%20so%20that%20our%20son%20could%20have%20a%20break%20while%20driving%2C%20and%20he%20unfortunately%20bit%20a%20librarian%20who%20was%20carrying%20him.%20She%20calmly%20told%20me%20that%20she%20had%20run%20story-times%20for%20three%20generations%20of%20families%20in%20the%20area%20and%20was%20used%20to%20her%20tiny%20clients%20biting%20her.%20She%20then%20encouraged%20us%20to%20take%20seeds%20from%20their%20seed%20library%20and%20see%20how%20they%20would%20do%20once%20we%20returned%20home.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EI%20met%20parents%20at%20a%20Duplo%20open%20play%20session%20at%20a%20library%20in%20Vancouver%2C%20Canada%2C%20who%20shared%20their%20hopes%2C%20dreams%2C%20worries%2C%20and%20anxieties%20about%20the%20future%20that%20their%20children%20would%20inherit.%20In%20Portland%2C%20Oregon%2C%20we%20stayed%20at%20a%20Harvest%20host%20site%20where%20our%20host%2C%20an%20ex-Peace%20Corp%20with%20two%20long%20gray%20pigtails%2C%20would%20carry%20our%20son%20down%20to%20the%20river%20and%20show%20him%20the%20deer%2C%20clad%20in%20a%20tie-dye%20print%20skirt%20from%20his%20days%20in%20Vietnam.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20Tahoe%2C%20we%20camped%20at%20a%20Thousand%20Trails%20campsite%20enveloped%20in%20tall%20pine%20trees%2C%20and%20I%20heard%20a%20familiar%20accent%20in%20the%20camping%20store%20that%20reminded%20me%20of%20home.%20There%20was%20a%20woman%20working%20there%20from%20Melbourne%2C%20Australia%2C%20where%20I%20had%20just%20spent%20the%20last%2010%20years%20living%20before%20I%20moved%20to%20the%20United%20States.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%20When%20we%20left%20Orlando%2C%20our%20son%20could%20sit%20up%20unassisted%20and%20had%20two%20teeth.%20When%20we%20returned%2C%20he%20was%20weeks%20away%20from%20walking%20and%20had%2010%20teeth%20and%20a%20lifetime%20of%20experiences.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20may%20not%20remember%20much%20of%20this%20trip%2C%20but%20we%20will.%20Living%20in%20an%20RV%20for%20three%20and%20a%20half%20months%20and%20traveling%20across%20the%20United%20States%20in%20it%20has%20taught%20us%20so%20much%20about%20living%20simply%2C%20making%20do%20with%20less%2C%20and%20the%20value%20of%20human%20connection.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-infant-on-a-four-month-rv-trip-across-us-2025-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740929642000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c1d9fb69253ccddf97e6ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftook-infant-on-a-four-month-rv-trip-across-us-2025-3%22%2