e%20became%20an%20unintended%20victim%20of%20the%20violence.%20Police%20suspect%20the%20attackers%20used%20a%20nunchuck%20--%20a%20weapon%20used%20in%20martial%20arts%20-%20to%20hit%20his%20skull.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShahabas%20died%20due%20to%20critical%20head%20injuries%20while%20undergoing%20treatment%20in%20the%20intensive%20care%20unit%20of%20Kozhikode%20Government%20Medical%20College%20Hospital.%20He%20died%20around%201%20am%20on%20Saturday.%20Following%20the%20incident%2C%20five%20students%20were%20taken%20into%20custody%2C%20charged%20with%20murder%20and%20presented%20before%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20postmortem%20report%20confirmed%20that%20Shahabas%20suffered%20a%20severe%20skull%20fracture%20and%20brain%20injuries%20caused%20by%20the%20attack.%20His%20body%20was%20taken%20to%20his%20ancestral%20home%20at%203%20pm%20after%20the%20postmortem%20at%20Kozhikode%20Medical%20College.%20It%20was%20kept%20for%20public%20viewing%20before%20being%20buried.%20Hundreds%2C%20including%20family%20and%20friends%2C%20gathered%20to%20pay%20their%20last%20respects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20police%2C%20during%20a%20dance%20performance%2C%20some%20students%20from%20Thamarassery%20Government%20Vocational%20Higher%20Secondary%20School%20mocked%20students%20from%20MJ%20Higher%20Secondary%20School.%20This%20led%20to%20tensions%20that%20escalated%20over%20the%20following%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20farewell%20event%2C%20students%20from%20different%20schools%20made%20social%20media%20posts%20on%20Instagram%20and%20gathered%20in%20town.%20On%20February%2027%2C%20around%2015%20students%2C%20including%20Shahabas%2C%20confronted%20the%20other%20group%20on%20Vezhuppur%20Road%20in%20Thamarassery%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20violent%20clash%20around%205%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20Shahabas%20did%20not%20appear%20to%20be%20seriously%20injured.%20He%20was%20taken%20to%20Thamarassery%20Taluk%20Hospital%20and%20then%20sent%20home.%20However%2C%20his%20condition%20worsened%2C%20and%20he%20was%20shifted%20to%20Kozhikode%20Medical%20College%20Hospital%2C%20where%20he%20remained%20in%20a%20coma%20until%20his%20death.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20based%20on%20a%20complaint%20by%20Shahabas's%20father.%20After%20his%20death%2C%20the%20charges%20were%20upgraded%20to%20murder.%20The%20parents%20of%20the%20accused%20have%20been%20instructed%20to%20present%20the%20students%20before%20the%20Juvenile%20Justice%20Board%20again.%20The%20police%20are%20also%20looking%20into%20whether%20others%20were%20involved.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKerala%20education%20minister%20V%20Sivankutty%20has%20ordered%20a%20departmental%20inquiry%20into%20the%20incident.%20The%20Director%20of%20Public%20Education%20has%20also%20called%20a%20detailed%20probe.%20%26quot%3BWhile%20cinema%20may%20have%20some%20influence%2C%20it's%20essential%20that%20everyone%20plays%20a%20role%20in%20uplifting%20society.%20No%20one%20should%20be%20led%20down%20the%20wrong%20path%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Union%20Minister%20Suresh%20Gopi.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740920460000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fl8fgcrr_kerala-student-death-_625x300_01_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-class-10-student-death-broken-skull-internal-bleeding-how-kerala-student-died-in-nunchuck-attack-7829895%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20postmortem%20report%20of%2016-year-old%20Muhammed%20Shahabas%2C%20who%20was%20brutally%20assaulted%20in%20Kerala's%20Kozhikode%20district%2C%20has%20revealed%20the%20extent%20of%20the%20attack.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fkerala-class-10-student-death-broken-skull-internal-bleeding-how-kerala-student-died-in-nunchuck-attack-7829895%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20key