ota%2C%20and%20Pennsylvania%20voting%20down%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20is%20resistance%20to%20crypto%20reserves%20among%20certain%20states%20primarily%20due%20to%20concerns%20over%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcrypto-bitcoin-volatility-financial-advisors-risks-digital-assets-speculation-tax-2025-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebitcoin's%20volatility%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20its%20suitability%20as%20a%20reserve%20asset%2C%26quot%3B%2021Shares%20crypto%20research%20strategist%20Matt%20Mena%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20flurry%20of%20downvotes%20has%20clouded%20what%20some%20analysts%20feel%20is%20a%20bullish%20development%20nationwide.%20Many%2C%20including%20Mena%2C%20have%20previously%20predicted%20that%20turning%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fcurrencies%2Fbtc-usd%3Futm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%26utm_medium%3Dingest%26utm_source%3Dmarkets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebitcoin%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20a%20reserve%20asset%20could%20spark%20a%20wave%20of%20similar%20moves%20globally%2C%20boosting%20the%20apex%20token's%20price%20dramatically%20as%20more%20governments%20buy%20the%20token.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIncluding%20the%20five%20states%20that%20voted%20against%20it%2C%2024%20governments%20have%20at%20least%20considered%20a%20digital%20assets%20reserve%2C%20with%20crypto%20often%20perceived%20as%20an%20inflation%20hedge%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Fbitcoin-price-rally-100000-gold-cryptocurrency-trump-microstrategy-treasury-asset-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epar%20with%20gold%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELawmakers%20have%20butted%20heads%20over%20whether%20crypto%20investments%20are%20a%20good%20use%20of%20taxpayer%20money.%20Criticism%20has%20focused%20on%20the%20volatility%20associated%20with%20the%20crypto%20tokens.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20legislative%20pushback%20doesn't%20appear%20to%20be%20partisan%2C%20either%2C%20with%20state-level%20Republicans%20voting%20alongside%20Democrats%20to%20reject%20these%20efforts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20signing%20on%20to%20that%20stuff%20and%20I%20can't%20imagine%20a%20majority%20of%20your%20constituents%20want%20you%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.binance.com%2Fen%2Fsquare%2Fpost%2F20763127695937%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ERepublican%20Bill%20Mercer%3C%2Fa%3E%20reportedly%20told%20the%20Montana%20House%20of%20Representatives%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYet%20industry%20advocates%20reject%20volatility%20as%20a%20viable%20argument%20to%20keep%20crypto%20out%20of%20government%20treasuries%2C%20and%20Mena%20noted%20that%20bitcoin%20has%20exhibited%20lower%20volatility%20than%20reserve%20assets%20such%20as%20oil%20at%20certain%20periods.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBitcoin%20has%20gone%20in%20one%20direction%20in%20the%20last%20number%20of%20years%2C%20and%20generally%20that's%20up%20and%20to%20the%20right%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Brian%20Morgenstern%2C%20head%20of%20public%20policy%20for%20Riot%20Platforms.%20While%20the%20dollar%20index%20has%20gained%20around%208.7%25%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years%2C%20bitcoin%20has%20soared%20over%20845%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20the%20concern%20about%20volatility%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20zoom%20out%20a%20little%20bit%20and%20when%20you%20do%20that%2C%20the%20value%20proposition%20becomes%20much%20more%20clear%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20a%20message%20at%20least%20some%20states%20are%20embracing%20even%20as%20others%20back%20away%20from%20crypto.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELegislators%20i%20Texas%20and%20Arizona%20are%20successfully%20pushing%20crypto%20reserve%20bills%20forward%2C%20and%20Utah%20appears%20set%20to%20be%20the%20first%20state%20poised%20to%20turn%20the%20idea%20into%20actual%20policy.%20If%20approved%2C%20its%20bill%20would%20allow%20the%20state%20t