0yard%2C%20and%20when%20my%20son's%20girlfriend%20tossed%20it%2C%20she%20accidentally%20took%20out%20a%20%24120%20bowl%20that%20was%20sitting%20on%20the%20table.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EShe%20was%20mortified%2C%20couldn't%20apologize%20enough%2C%20and%20asked%20me%20where%20she%20could%20find%20a%20replacement.%20I%20did%20everything%20I%20could%20to%20reassure%20her%20that%20I%20wasn't%20angry%2C%20and%20I%20honestly%20just%20gave%20her%20the%20purchase%20details%20because%20it%20seemed%20like%20the%20quickest%20way%20to%20stop%20her%20from%20feeling%20so%20badly%20about%20it.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20guess%20she%20had%20no%20idea%20how%20much%20it%20would%20cost%20because%20although%20she%20ordered%20me%20a%20new%20one%20and%20had%20it%20shipped%20to%20me%20directly%2C%20my%20son%20called%20me%20upset%20over%20making%20her%20spend%20so%20much%20on%20what%20was%20an%20accident.%20He%20brought%20up%20the%20time%20my%20dog%20chewed%20up%20his%20girlfriend's%20purse%2C%20which%20was%20apparently%20worth%20several%20hundred%20dollars%2C%20and%20they%20hadn't%20told%20me%20because%20they%20didn't%20want%20to%20stress%20me%20out.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20don't%20know%20what%20to%20do.%20Should%20I%20pay%20her%20back%20for%20the%20bowl%3F%20Should%20I%20offer%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20purse%3F%20I%20hate%20that%20they're%20angry%20at%20me%2C%20but%20they're%20also%20adults%20and%20should%20be%20able%20to%20stand%20by%20their%20decisions.%20I%20feel%20like%20they%20are%20going%20to%20be%20mad%20at%20me%20no%20matter%20what%20I%20do.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3ESincerely%2C%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%3Cstrong%3EJust%20Want%20Everyone%20to%20be%20Happy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDear%20Just%20Want%2C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIf%20you%20don't