on-the-ground%20guides%20and%20brought%20to%20a%20remote%20location%20over%20a%20day%20or%20more%20of%20travel%2C%20which%20could%20be%20by%20car%2C%20aircraft%2C%20four-by-four%2C%20or%20even%20yak.%20Then%20they%20typically%20undergo%20a%20day%20or%20two%20of%20basic%20survival%20training%20%E2%80%94%20learning%20things%20like%20how%20to%20build%20a%20fire%2C%20construct%20a%20shelter%2C%20or%20dig%20a%20hole%20in%20the%20ground%20to%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20training%2C%20the%20traveler%2C%20equipped%20with%20supplies%20that%20includes%20a%20map%20and%20compass%2C%20will%20split%20up%20from%20their%20guides%20and%20be%20left%20all%20alone%20to%20navigate%20themselves%20back%20to%20civilization%20over%20the%20course%20of%20several%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Esther%20Spengler%20sitting%20and%20looking%20out%20at%20the%20desert.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F67c2423b69253ccddf97fda8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EEsther%20Spengler%20pictured%20at%20the%20end%20of%20her%20solo%20trek%20after%20meeting%20back%20up%20with%20her%20guide.%3Cp%3EEsther%20Spengler%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2277f32f68-84c0-4ef3-a330-19f4983998ab%5C%22%3ETravel%20as%20'therapy'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20the%20person%20on%20the%20trip%20may%20feel%20totally%20isolated%2C%20Black%20Tomato%20is%20always%20tracking%20them%20visually%20and%20with%20satellite%20communication%20devices.%20The%20guides%20are%20on%20the%20ground%20trekking%20along%20%E2%80%94%20often%20with%20the%20client%20literally%20in%20their%20line%20of%20sight%2C%20even%20though%20the%20client%20can't%20see%20them%20%E2%80%94%20so%20that%20they%20can%20intervene%20if%20needed%20for%20safety%20reasons.%20Altogether%2C%20the%20trips%20require%20months%20of%20meticulous%20planning%20by%20Black%20Tomato%2C%20Murray-John%20said.%3C%2Fp