0really%20important%2C%26quot%3B%20Linsky%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe're%20on%20the%20path%20towards%20full%20agentic%20workflows%2C%26quot%3B%20Linsky%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe're%20definitely%20not%20replacing%20our%20investment%20associates%20with%20the%20capabilities%20right%20now%2C%20but%20it%20is%20helping%20to%20speed%20along%20their%20process.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227bd475dd-0876-4748-9df4-3db5787a7683%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMUFG%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAWS%20focus%20area%3A%20turning%20multiple%20data%20sets%20into%20new%20sales%20ideas%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMitsubishi%20UFJ%20Financial%20Group%2C%20which%20offers%20everything%20from%20investment%20banking%20to%20treasury%20management%20and%20trade%20finance%2C%20is%20using%20generative%20AI%20to%20give%20its%20corporate%20salespeople%20a%20leg%20up.%20An%20AI%20platform%20that%20suggests%20sales%20ideas%20has%20led%20to%20a%2030%25%20conversion%20rate%2C%20Tetsuo%20Horigane%2C%20head%20of%20quant%20innovation%20at%20MUFG%2C%20said%20at%20re%3AInvent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22MUFG%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5c1944adb3c21d6b690e07a7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221368%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMitsubishi%20UFJ%20Financial%20Group%20(MUFG)%20is%20a%20large%20Japanese%20bank.%3Cp%3EKazuhiro%20Nogi%2FAFP%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMUFG%20began%20developing%20generative%20AI%20applications%20in%202023%20after%20launching%20an%20in-house%20AI%2FML%20team%20two%20years%20prior%2C%20Horigane%20said.%20MUFG%20also%20has%20about%202%2C000%20employees%20serving%20roughly%201%20million%20corporate%20clients%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank's%20salespeople%20typically%20read%20through%20hundreds%20or%20thousands%20of%20pages%20of%20documents%20to%20understand%20a%20given%20client's%20situation%20and%20what%20financial%20product%20is%20most%20relevant%20to%20them.%20But%20now%20the%20AI%20platform%20combines%20multiple%20data%20sets%2C%20like%20the%20client's%20transaction%20history%2C%20previous%20sales%20conversions%20to%20understand%20what%20they're%20in%20the%20market%20for%2C%20their%20financial%20filings%2C%20and%20public%20information%20like%20news%2C%20Kain%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20process%20of%20drafting%20a%20sales%20pitch%2C%20which%20could%20take%20several%20hours%20or%20days%2C%20could%20now%20be%20done%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20minutes%2C%20Horigane%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22483702d1-5958-4dc2-a0f3-1ed14965ac9c%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAWS%20focus%20area%3A%20using%20call%20center%20AI%20to%20influence%20strategy%20and%20experience%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAI%20in%20call%20centers%20is%20nothing%20novel%2C%20but%20for%20Rocket%20Mortgage%2C%20it's%20leading%20executives%20to%20think%20about%20whole%20new%20strategies%20and%20experiences.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20fintech%20integrated%20AWS's%20generative%20AI%20technology%20into%20its%20call%20centers%20to%20lessen%20the%20load%20for%20its%20thousands%20of%20call%20center%20employees%20who%20field%20calls%2C%20emails%2C%20and%20webchats%20every%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20idea%20is%20not%20just%20to%20have%20one%20AI%20assistant%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Ban%20entire%20network%20of%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20Dan%20Vasquez%2C%20VP%20of%20AI%20strategy%20at%20Rocket%20Mortgage%2C%20said%20at%20re%3AInvent.%20They%20help%20with%20transcribing%2C%20picking%20out%20key%20pieces%20of%20information%20mid-call%2C%20and%20providing%20insights%20and%20data%20about%20the%20call%20after%20the%20fact%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGenerative%20AI%20has%20helped%20save%20some%2040%2C000%20hours%20annually%20for%20call%20center%20employees%20and%20enabled%2070%25%20of%20client%20support%20to%20be%20fully%20self-served%2C%20Vasquez%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20now%2C%20Rocket%20Mortgage%20is%20using%20those%2010%20petabytes%20of%20data%20to%20figure%20out%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20should%20we%20do%20next%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20the%20real%20benefit%2C%20Kain%20said%2C%20for%20the%20fintech%20to%20start%20asking%20big%20questions%20like%20%26quot%3Bwhy%20are%20my%20customers%20calling%20me%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20are%20my%20most%20common%20problems%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20use%20that%20intel%20to%20rethink%20its%20online%20platforms%2C%20streamline%20workflows%2C%20and%20improve%20the%20overall%20customer%20experience.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-wall-street-jpmorgan-bridgewater-mufg-rocket-mortgage-2025-2%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740916802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6765ac3f6c531c315b8997bc%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-wall-street-jpmorgan-bridgewater-mufg-rocket-mortgage-2025-2%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22From%20boosting%20corporate%20sales%20at%20MUFG%20to%20giving%20Bridgewater%20tools%20to%20build%20an%20AI%20investment%20analyst%2C%20here's%20how%20AWS%20is%20helping%20finance%20giants%20with%20AI.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Bianca%20Chan)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A25%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws-wall-street-jpmorgan-bridgewater-mufg-rocket-mortgage-2025-2%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Kerala%20Architect%20Builds%20Breathtaking%2C%20Sustainable%20Home%20Without%20Cutting%20Down%20a%20Single%20Tree!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20heart%20of%20Kerala%E2%80%99s%20Kozhinjampara%2C%20architect%20Petchimuthu%20Kennedy%20has%20lent%20a%20new%20and%20refreshing%20definition%20to%20sustainable%20living%20with%20his%20unique%20%E2%80%98Wendy%20House%E2%80%99.%C2%A0%20Built%20without%20cutting%20do