Fworld-news%2Fdramatic-footage-shows-cruise-ship-tilting-sideways-injuring-16-passengers-7829729%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20video%20showed%20kitchen%20staff%20clinging%20to%20counters%20for%20balance%20as%20equipment%20crashed%20to%20the%20floor%2C%20food%20spilt%20everywhere%2C%20and%20broken%20dishes%20littered%20the%20ground.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdramatic-footage-shows-cruise-ship-tilting-sideways-injuring-16-passengers-7829729%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Trump-Zelensky%20Row%20Prompts%20Europe%20To%20Regroup%2C%20Evaluate%20Its%20Security%20Options%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20very%20public%20clash%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Ukraine's%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20received%20a%20royal%20welcome%20in%20Britain%2C%20as%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20demonstrate%20their%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%26quot%3B%20support%20to%20him.%20The%20Ukrainian%20president%20is%20in%20London%20to%20attend%20a%20summit%20hosted%20by%20UK%20Prime%20Minister%20Keir%20Starmer%2C%20where%20he's%20also%20set%20to%20hold%20an%20official%20audience%20with%20at%20Sandringham.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Friday's%20extraordinary%20scenes%20in%20the%20Oval%20Office%20will%20now%20likely%20dominate%20the%20agenda%20of%20Zelensky's%20London%20visit%2C%20and%20refocus%20the%20conversation%20on%20how%20Europe%20and%20Ukraine%20can%20get%20the%20US%20back%20on%20side%20as%20a%20security%20guarantor%20for%20any%20peace%20deal%20with%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20White%20House%20row%2C%20the%20European%20leaders%2C%20including%20those%20from%20Germany%2C%20France%2C%20Spain%2C%20Poland%2C%20and%20the%20Netherlands%2C%20have%20posted%20social%20media%20messages%20backing%20Ukraine%20-%20with%20Zelensky%20responding%20directly%20to%20each%20one%20to%20thank%20them%20for%20their%20support.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20Trump%20administration's%20sudden%20detente%20with%20Russia%2C%20which%20started%20with%20a%20phone%20call%20between%20Trump%20and%20Putin%2C%20and%20then%20the%20beginning%20of%20initial%20talks%20with%20senior%20Russian%20officials%20over%20ending%20the%20war%20sidelining%20the%20Europeans%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20before%20the%20humiliating%20scenes%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20has%20jolted%20European%20governments%20into%20action%20with%20fear%20that%20the%20United%20States%20may%20abandon%20Europe%20altogether.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20worry%20that%20if%20the%20Trump%20administration%20forces%20a%20weak%20peace%20deal%20over%20Ukraine%2C%20it%20would%20embolden%20Russia%2C%20making%20Moscow%20a%20bigger%20threat%20to%20the%20rest%20of%20Europe.%20The%20change%20in%20America's%20stance%20has%20also%20made%20achieving%20greater%20self-reliance%20for%20Europe%20more%20urgent%20than%20ever.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EEuropean%20Concerns%C2%A0%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20United%20States%20alone%20has%20spent%20about%20%24114%20billion%20on%20aid%20for%20Ukraine%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20war%20three%20years%20ago%2C%20compared%20to%20Europe's%20%24132%20billion%2C%20according%20to%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22No%20Follow%2C%20No%20Index%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2025%2F03%2F02%2Fworld%2Feurope%2Fukraine-trump.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times.%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithout%20American%20support%2C%20if%20Russia%20breaks%20the%20ceasefire%20agreement%2C%20the%20odds%20of%20stopping%20Kermelin%20forces%20would%20be%20significantly%20reduced%2C%20leaving%20European%20troops%20in%20Ukraine%20-%20stationed%20at%20key%20Ukrainian%20infrastructure%20sites%20-%20more%20exposed%20to%20probing%20Russian%20aggression.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat's%20why%2C%20despite%20Friday's%20fall%2C%20Ukraine%20is%20still%20seeking%20a%20security%20guarantee%20from%20Washington%20to%20deter%20Russia%20from%20relaunching%20its%20war%20in%20the%20near%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20top%20European%20officials%20are%20meeting%20this%20week%20to%20discuss%20defense%2C%20first%20in%20London%20on%20Sunday%2C%20and%20then%20in%20Brussels%20on%20Thursday%20at%20a%20special%20summit%20of%20the%20European%20Council%20to%20discuss%20the%20proposal%20to%20beef%20up%20EU%20defenses%20faster%20than%20previously%20expected%2C%20and%20to%20more%20clearly%20define%20possible%20security%20guarantees%20for%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBuilding%20an%20independent%20European%20defence%20architecture%20is%20the%20second%20and%20longer-term%20security%20concern%20for%20Europe.%20Almost%2080%20years%20after%20the%20end%20of%20World%20War%20II%2C%20America%20still%20maintains%20over%2030%20military%20bases%20across%20Europe%2C%20including%20in%20Germany%20and%20Britain%2C%20where%20over%2060%2C000%20military%20personnel%20are%20stationed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20NYT%20report%2C%20EU%20nations%20have%20been%20increasing%20their%20military%20spending%20in%20recent%20years%20-%20spending%2030%20percent%20more%20last%20year%20than%20in%202021.%20Despite%20that%2C%20some%20NATO%20countries%2C%20including%20France%20and%20Germany%2C%20are%20still%20short%20of%20the%20goal%20of%20members'%20spending%202%20per%20cent%20or%20more%20of%20their%20gross%20domestic%20product%20on%20defense%2C%20leaving%20it%20to%20the%20US%20to%20prop%20up%20the%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETrump's%20America%20has%20made%20it%20clear%20that%20it%20wants%20Europe%20to%20spend%20more%20on%20their%20own%20defence%2C%20and%20be%20the%20majority%20stakeholder%20in%20maintaining%20the%20peace%20in%20Ukraine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20just%20not%20fair%20or%20sustainable%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20US%20Secretary%20of%20State%20Marco%20Rubio%20in%20an%20interview%20with%20Fox%20News%20this%20week%20describing%20the%20outsized%20role%20that%20the%20US%20has%20played%20in%20funding%20NATO%20for%20years%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20it%20would%20likely%20take%20years%20for%20Europe%20to%20build%20the%20weapons%20systems%20and%20capabilities%20needed%20to%20be%20truly%20independent%20militarily.%20But%20the%20Friday's%20row%20has%20prompted%20calls%20for%20fast%20action%2C%20with%20some%20European%20leaders%20hoping%20that%20even%20countries%20that%20have%20been%20reluctant%20to%20increase%20the%20defence%20spending%20and%20support%20for%20Ukraine%20will%20now%20get%20on%20board%20with%20a%20more%20ambitious%20approach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20powerful%20Europe%2C%20we%20need%20it%20more%20than%20ever%2C%26quot%3B%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20of%20France%20posted%20on%20social%20media.%20%26quot%3BThe%20surge%20is%20now.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740912240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2025-03%2Fjiqm9oa_keir-starmer-volodymyr-zelensky_625x300_02_March_25.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-volodymyr-zelensky-row-prompts-europe-to-regroup-evaluate-its-securityoptions-7829773%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20a%20very%20public%20clash%20with%20US%20President%20Donald%20Trump%20at%20the%20White%20House%2C%20Ukraine's%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20received%20a%20royal%20welcome%20in%20Britain%2C%20as%20the%20United%20Kingdom%20and%20the%20European%20Union%20demonstrate%20their%20%26quot%3Bunwavering%26quot%3B%20support%20to%20him.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fdonald-trump-volodymyr-zelensky-row-prompts-europe-to-regroup-evaluate-its-securityoptions-7829773%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Private%20spacecraft%20Blue%20Ghost%20lands%20on%20Moon%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740912227000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3