olice%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20come%20as%20a%20mother%20seeking%20justice%2C%20not%20as%20a%20Union%20Minister%20and%20MP%2C%26quot%3B%20added%20a%20visibly%20upset%20Ms%20Khadse.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKushanat%20Pingde%2C%20Deputy%20Superintendent%20of%20Police%2C%20Muktainagar%20said%20that%20the%20accused%20misbehaved%20with%20several%20girls%20and%20even%20clashed%20with%20their%20bodyguards%20when%20they%20tried%20to%20intervene.%20He%20has%20named%20seven%20accused%20in%20the%20case%2C%20of%20whom%20one%20has%20been%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDenying%20any%20political%20pressure%2C%20he%20said%20a%20case%20has%20been%20lodged%20for%20molestation%2C%20and%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act.%20Charges%20under%20the%20IT%20Act%20have%20also%20been%20added%20since%20the%20accused%20also%20clicked%20the%20girls'%20videos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%2C%20Ms%20Khadse%20-%20who%20belongs%20to%20the%20BJP%2C%20that's%20in%20power%20in%20Maharashtra%20-%20raised%20a%20concern%20over%20the%20safety%20of%20the%20common%20people%20when%20even%20ministers'%20families%20are%20not%20safe.%20She%20asked%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20my%20own%20daughter%20is%20not%20safe%2C%20what%20will%20be%20the%20condition%20of%20others%3F%20I%20will%20demand%20strict%20action%20from%20the%20state%20government%20for%20the%20implementation%20of%20the%20law.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20daughter%20of%20a%20public%20representative%20is%20being%20harassed%2C%20then%20what%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20common%20citizens%3F%26quot%3B%20she%20sought%20to%20know.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Khadse%2C%20a%20three-time%20MP%20from%20the%20Raver%20seat%2C%20said%20crimes%20against%20women%20have%20increased%20across%20Maharashtra%20and%20there%20is%20no%20fear%20of%20law.%20Many%20girls%20hesitate%20to%20come%20forward%2C%20but%20we%20must%20not%20stay%20silent%2C%20she%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20she%20would%20meet%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20de