0leaders%20from%20across%20the%20country.%20The%20meeting%20reviewed%20the%20strategy%20of%20BSP%2C%20which%20has%20been%20struggling%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh%2C%20which%20it%20ruled%20in%20the%20past%2C%20and%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Chequered%20Journey%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAkash%20Anand%2C%20who%20studied%20in%20Delhi%20and%20Noida%20before%20completing%20his%20MBA%20from%20the%20UK's%20University%20of%20Plymouth%2C%20was%20showcased%20as%20the%20BSP's%20future%20and%20Ms%20Mayawati's%20political%20heir.%20He%20first%20emerged%20on%20the%20political%20scene%20ahead%20of%20the%202019%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls.%20Positioned%20as%20a%20new-age%20face%2C%20he%20is%20considered%20to%20have%20played%20a%20key%20role%20in%20pushing%20BSP's%20social%20media%20presence.%20Towards%20the%20end%20of%202023%2C%20he%20was%20appointed%20the%20party's%20national%20coordinator%2C%20officially%20establishing%20him%20as%20Number%202%20in%20BSP.%20However%2C%20shortly%20before%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%20last%20year%2C%20Mayawati%20removed%20him%20from%20the%20top%20post%2C%20saying%20he%20needed%20%26quot%3Bmaturity%26quot%3B.%20Akash's%20father%20replaced%20him.%20The%20BSP%20was%20routed%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20winning%20zero%20seats.%20Soon%20after%2C%20Akash%20Anand%20was%20reappointed%20as%20national%20coordinator%20in%20June.%20Now%2C%20eight%20months%20later%2C%20he%20is%20out%20again.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Mayawati%20said%20she%20would%20name%20anyone%20her%20political%20heir%20and%20added%20that%20her%20family%20will%20not%20forge%20any%20ties%20with%20another%20political%20family%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Build-Up%20And%20A%20Big%20Hint%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20clear%20indication%20of%20Akash%20Anand%20losing%20favour%20with%20the%20BSP%20chief%20came%20last%20month%20when%20his%20father-in-law%20Ashok%20Siddharth%20was%20expelled%20from%20the%20BSP%20for%20anti-party%20activities.%20In%20a%20post%20on%20X%2C%20Ms%20Mayawati%20said%20former%20MP%20Siddharth%20and%20Nitin%20Singh%20had%20been%20expelled%20for%20factionalism%20and%20other%20anti-party%20activities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20later%2C%20the%20BSP%20chief%20dropped%20a%20big%20hint.%20She%20said%20in%20a%20long%20thread%20that%20as%20the%20political%20heir%20of%20BSP%20founder%20Kanshi%20Ram%2C%20she%20would%20struggle%20lifelong%20to%20free%20Dalits%20from%20political%20slavery%20and%20social%20helplessness.%20Without%20taking%20names%2C%20she%20added%20that%20her%20true%20heir%20could%20only%20be%20someone%20committed%20to%20taking%20the%20movement%20forward%20despite%20all%20odds.%20The%20remark%20was%20seen%20as%20a%20swipe%20to%20Akash%20Anand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EA%20Floundering%20Political%20Force%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20BSP's%20leadership%20flip-flops%20are%20playing%20out%20against%20the%20backdrop%20of%20its%20massive%20electoral%20setbacks%20over%20the%20past%20few%20years%20that%20have%20raised%20questions%20about%20its%20political%20future.%20The%20BSP%2C%20which%20won%20206%20seats%20in%20the%20Uttar%20Pradesh%20Assembly%20in%202007%2C%20won%20just%20one%20seat%20in%20the%202022%20state%20polls.%20In%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20the%20party%20won%2010%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20polls%2C%20when%20it%20contested%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Samajwadi%20Party.%20This%20time%2C%20it%20decided%20to%20go%20solo%20and%20drew%20a%20blank%20and%20new%20political%20forces%20such%20as%20the%20Chandrashekar%20Azad-led%20Azad%20Samaj%20Party%20dented%20the%20BSP's%20traditional%20support%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1740908940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fsef5k7h8_mayawati-with-nephew-and-political-heir-akash-anand-ians_625x300_08_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmayawati-akash-anand-in-out-in-out-mayawatis-nephew-loses-top-party-post-