another%20person%20make%20the%20stand%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%224678180483%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20only%20person%20involved%20in%20the%20design%2C%20Tharun%20takes%20care%20of%20the%20woodwork%2C%20while%20outsourcing%20experts%20from%20Chennai%2C%20Pondicherry%2C%20and%20Madurai%20to%20carve%20wings%2C%20the%20body%20etc.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20are%20the%20best%20people%20in%20Tamil%20Nadu%2C%20and%20people%20who%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20craft%20are%20just%20a%20handful%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Tharun.%20He%20adds%20that%20around%2030%20people%20are%20involved%20in%20the%20manufacturing%20ecosystem.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20best%20part%20%E2%80%94%20all%20of%20the%20instruments%20are%20handcrafted%20with%20precision%20to%20detail.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20CMC%20machines%20involved.%20The%20carving%20is%20handmade%2C%20and%20the%20machines%20used%20are%20just%20hand%20tools%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20the%20instrument%E2%80%99s%20sound%2C%20Tharun%20relied%20on%20literary%20descriptions%20and%20a%20book%20titled%20%3Cem%3EYazh%20Nool%20%3C%2Fem%3E(1947)%20by%20Vipulananda%20Adigalar.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20parts%20of%20the%20Yazh%20were%20mentioned%20in%20the%20book%20like%3Cem%3E%20Athar%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20resonator)%2C%20%3Cem%3EThandu%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20part%20where%20you%20tie%20the%20strings)%2C%20%3Cem%3EAani%3C%2Fem%3E%20(a%20tuning%20key)%2C%20and%20the%20like.%20Based%20on%20the%20usage%20of%20the%20parts%2C%20we%20can%20understand%20how%20the%20instrument%20would%20have%20sounded%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%2