ock-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20call%20it%20SK-4%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%202008%2C%20Karekar%20was%20able%20to%20develop%20a%20superior%20clone%20with%20all%20the%20desired%20traits%20and%20named%20it%20SK-4%2C%20taking%20the%20first%20letter%20of%20Shendge%20Kaka%2C%20the%20farmer%20who%20initially%20gave%20him%20tubers%20of%20Sangli%20Kadapa%20variety%2C%20Special%20Konkan%2C%20and%20his%20own%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%229253875046%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202020%20Kharif%20season%2C%20the%20Dapoli-based%20Dr%20Balasaheb%20Sawant%20Konkan%20Krishi%20Vidyapeeth%20(DBSKKV)%20carried%20out%20validation%20trials%20at%20the%20National%20Innovation%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20(NIF)%20behest.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnif.org.in%2Finnovation%2Fimproved-high-yielding-turmeric-variety%2F1143%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENIF%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20variety%20was%20promising%2C%20with%20a%20high%20rhizome%20yield%20(56t%2Fha).%20Among%20the%2032%20tested%20varieties%2C%20SK-4%20was%20observed%20to%20be%20superior%20over%2028%20check%20varieties%20and%20at%20par%20with%20the%20best%20check%20variety%20Sona%20(64t%2Fha)%2C%20in%20terms%20of%20yield%2Fha.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Sachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20stands%20beside%20a%20harvest%20of%20the%20SK-4%20turmeric%20variety%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839.jpg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-300x135.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-500x225.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-768x346.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-1200x540.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FSachin-Karekar-with-his-SK-4-turmeric-variety-1740635839-150x68.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-410068%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22576%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESachin%20Kamlakar%20Karekar%20stands%20beside%20a%20harvest%20of%20the%20SK-4%20turmeric%20variety%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COur%20trials%20were%20spread%20over%20two%20years%20and%20we%20found%20that%20SK-4%20was%20characterised%20by%20its%20high%20yield%20potential%2C%20like%20Rajendra%20Sona.%20The%20latter%E2%80%99s%20seed%20material%20is%20always%20scarce%20and%20we%20hope%20the%20new%20variety%20will%20fulfil%20the%20demand.%20SK-4%20is%20a%20good%20alternative%20for%20those%20growing%20it%20in%20Konkan%E2%80%99s%20high-rainfall%20region.%20Incidentally%2C%20the%20variety%20is%20yet%20to%20be%20evaluated%20in%20low%20rainfall%20areas%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Dr%20Prafulla%20Mali%2C%20horticulturist%2C%20DBSKKV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdi