a.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F02%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-02-24-at-15.53.55_11zon-1-1740399732-150x100.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-409024%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22853%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20couple%20manages%20funds%20for%20the%20work%20with%20the%20help%20of%20CSR%20backing%20by%20corporations%20and%20funds%20raised%20by%20individuals.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuoting%20the%20example%20of%20the%20tigress%20they%20spotted%20in%20Kanha%2C%20the%20couple%20aimed%20to%20harness%20renewable%20energy%20to%20address%20water%20scarcity%20in%20the%20wild.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%3Cins%20data-ad-slot%3D%5C%227521127830%5C%22%20data-ad-client%3D%5C%22ca-pub-5691287967087057%5C%22%20data-ad-format%3D%5C%22fluid%5C%22%20data-ad-layout%3D%5C%22in-article%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20providing%20solar-powered%20pumps%2C%20which%20are%20submerged%20in%20borewells%20or%20perennial%20water%20bodies%20inside%20the%20forest%2C%20water%20is%20drawn%20out%20using%20solar%20energy%20and%20distributed%20through%20underground%20pipelines%20to%20various%20water%20bodies.%20This%20ensures%20that%20different%20animals%20have%20access%20to%20water%20within%20their%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F306700%2Fgrass-man-of-india-creates-grasslands-habiats-for-tigers-cheetahs-across-india-dr-gajanan-muratkar%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enatural%20habitat%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20process%20was%20rigorous%2C%20requiring%20complex%20logistics%20in%20remote%20and%20restricted%20areas%2C%20often%20under%20challenging%20conditions.%20Each%20installation%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20just%20about%20placing%20a%20pump%20in%20a%20borewell%20%E2%80%93%20sometimes%20in%20water%20bodies%20full%20of%20crocodiles%20or%20down%20a%20steep%20cliff%20of%20a%20waterfall.%20It%20involved%20s